compareTo(Element) - Method in class afterSOLIDrevisionEHL.model.Book
Sorts instances of Book by lexicological order of their author's name (using the method compareTo of class String); if two instances of Book have the same author, they will be sorted by lexicologically order of the title (using the method compareTo of class String).
compareTo(Element) - Method in class afterSOLIDrevisionEHL.model.CD
Sorts instances of CD by descending order of number of tracks; if two instances of CD have the same number of tracks, they are lexicologically ordered by their title.
compareTo(Element) - Method in class afterSOLIDrevisionEHL.model.DVD
Sorts instances of DVD by ascending ordered of their duration; if two instances of DVD have the same duration, they are lexicologically ordered by their title.
compareTo(Element) - Method in class afterSOLIDrevisionEHL.model.Element
Sorts instances of Element by lexicological order of the field title (using the method compareTo of class String); if two instances have the same title , they will be sorted by lexicological order of the String representation of their classes (obtained using the methods getClass of class Object, toString of class Class and compareTo of class String).
